## Video drivers/hardware acceleration. Please avoid translating 'OpenGL' and 'ANGLE'.

preferences-video-driver = Video drajver
preferences-video-driver-opengl-mac = OpenGL (preporučeno na Mac računalima)
preferences-video-driver-software-mac = Softver (ne preporučuje se)
preferences-video-driver-opengl-other = OpenGL (brži, može uzrokovati probleme)
preferences-video-driver-software-other = Softver (sporiji)
preferences-video-driver-angle = ANGLE (možda radi bolje od OpenGL-a)
preferences-video-driver-default = zadano
